OL,4,Ctraps come into force
OL,6,FNew laws aimed at protecting animals
OL,7,Fin Guernsey have come into force.
OL,9,FThe Animal Welfare (Guernsey)
OL,10,F(Amendment) Ordinance, 2025 places
OL,11,Frestrictions on snares, glue traps and
OL,12,Flamping - the practice of using bright
OL,13,Flights to dazzle hunted animals.
OL,15,FThe changes also give greater
OL,16,Fenforcement powers for animal welfare
OL,17,Finvestigations.
