OL,3,CLaws banning snares and other animal
OL,4,Ctraps come into force
OL,6,FDeputy Lindsay de Sausmarez, President
OL,7,Fof the Committee, said: "The Ordinance
OL,8,Fwill have a notably positive effect on
OL,9,Fthe lives of Guernsey's animals,
OL,10,Faligning with legislative advancements
OL,11,Felsewhere in recognition of animal
OL,12,Fsentience and helping fulfil our
OL,13,Finternational Conventions and trade
OL,14,Fagreement obligations."
OL,16,FThe proposals were put forward by the
OL,17,FCommittee for the Environment &
OL,18,FInfrastructure and got approved by the
OL,19,Fisland's assembly in July 2024.
OL,21,FWhat are the new laws?
