OL,3,CLaws banning snares and other animal
OL,4,Ctraps come into force
OL,6,FAs of 1st May 2025, it is an offence
OL,7,Fto:
OL,9,FCertain stunning and slaughtering
OL,10,Fdevices that do not meet humane
OL,11,Fstandards for culling birds and small
OL,12,Fmammals are also prohibited.
OL,14,FThe laws also prevent the farming of
OL,15,Fanimals for fur, feathers and down or
OL,16,Fhides and skin as a primary product.
OL,18,FThe production of foie gras by force-
OL,19,Ffeeding and using wild animals in
OL,20,Fcircuses is also banned.
