OL,3,CLaws banning snares and other animal
OL,4,Ctraps come into force
OL,6,FInsect traps are still allowed,
OL,7,Fhowever they must be set up in a way
OL,8,Fthat won't lead to larger animals
OL,9,Fbecoming caught in them.
OL,11,FMore information on the new laws can
OL,12,Fbe found on the States of Guernsey
OL,13,Fwebsite.
